    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="186"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d186">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.4016 <gloss target="#t_DP1"
                    >DP</gloss>/7–545</note>
                <head>No. 186 <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Czechoslovakia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_KAW1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Klieforth</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/> No. 42</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Praha</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-05">July 5,
                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">Subject: Czechoslovakia’s desire to have application for
                    transfer of minorities placed on agenda for forthcoming meeting of Big
                    Three.</p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: With reference to my telegram No. 59 of July 4,
                        1945,<note n="1" xml:id="d186fn1">Not printed. This telegram transmitted a
                        telegraphic text of the enclosure to the despatch here printed. For the text
                        of the enclosure, see <ref target="#d439">document No. 439</ref>.</note> 1
                    have the honor to transmit herewith a copy of the Foreign Office note in English
                    expressing the desire of the President<note n="2" xml:id="d186fn2">
                        <persName corresp="#p_BE2">Edvard Beneš</persName>.</note> and Government of
                    Czechoslovakia to have the application for the transfer of the minorities placed
                    on the agenda at the forthcoming meeting of President <persName
                        corresp="#p_THS1">Truman</persName>, Prime Minister <persName
                        corresp="#p_CMWS1">Churchill</persName> and <persName corresp="#p_SMIV2"
                        >Marshal Stalin</persName>.</p>
                <p>Respectfully yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_KAW1">A W <hi rend="smallcaps">Klieforth</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
